This paper deals with a computer vision problem of reconstructing tile panels, which involves image processing and pattern recognition. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also uses genetic algorithms and deep learning, which are subfields of artificial intelligence, so cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also a likely category. The problem of reconstructing tile panels is related to graphics and visualization, so cs.GR (Graphics) is another possible category. The paper also involves optimization and search algorithms, which are topics in machine learning, so cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category. Finally, the paper involves image analysis and processing, which is a topic in multimedia, so cs.MM (Multimedia) is another possible category.
